        {
            "title": "紅磡首岸上載樓書   價單下周公布",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15851836&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒地(00012)牽頭的紅磡庇利街大型重建項目首岸第1期及第3期今天上載樓書，擬下周公布首張價單。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">首岸第1期及第3期今天上載樓書，合共提供648伙，擬下周開放示範單位及開價，價錢參考同區新盤等。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">首岸第1期屬於第2座，提供360伙，實用面積301至642方呎；首岸第3期屬於第1座，提供288伙，實用面積301至708方呎。 </p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15851836-%e7%b4%85%e7%a3%a1%e9%a6%96%e5%b2%b8%e4%b8%8a%e8%bc%89%e6%a8%93%e6%9b%b8-%e5%83%b9%e5%96%ae%e4%b8%8b%e5%91%a8%e5%85%ac%e5%b8%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_NEW-FLAT_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 08:21:15",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "啟德海灣二期公布首張價單  折實價560萬起 呎價23888元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15851819&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">嘉華國際(00173)、會德豐地產、中海外(00688)合作發展啟德海灣第二期開布首張價單，涉及225伙單位，入場單位由560萬元起。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">首張價單涵蓋83伙一房單位、81伙兩房單位，61伙三房單位，實用面積由278平方呎至771平方呎，折實售價由560萬元至2929.8萬元，折實平均呎價23888元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">最低售價單位為第1C座6樓G室，實用面積306平方呎，屬一房單位，扣除最高25%折扣後，折實價560萬元，呎價18301元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">入場兩房單位為第1C座5樓E室，實用面積443平方呎，扣除最高折扣25%後，折實價798.8萬元，呎價18032元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15851819-%e5%95%9f%e5%be%b7%e6%b5%b7%e7%81%a3%e4%ba%8c%e6%9c%9f%e5%85%ac%e5%b8%83%e9%a6%96%e5%bc%b5%e5%83%b9%e5%96%ae-%e6%8a%98%e5%af%a6%e5%83%b9560%e8%90%ac%e8%b5%b7-%e5%91%8e%e5%83%b923888%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/pp_new-flat-transaction_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 08:21:15",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "代理料次季約15新盤登場 一手交投料穩守6000宗",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15851633&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">本港樓市氣氛持續向好，據物業代理統計，今年首季一手住宅成交約6300宗，按年增加逾40%。踏入第二季，發展商推盤步伐積極，市場估計本月將有9個新盤推出，合共涉及逾3600個單位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美聯物業高級董事布少明相信，第二季新盤市場將持續活躍，預計將有約15個新盤推出市場，數量不會低於首季。他估計今季一手交投將維持在6000宗左右，即每月平均成交約2000宗，並維持今年整體樓價升10%至15%的預測。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">布少明分析，個別大型樓盤的發展商會先以招標形式推售面積較大、景觀較好的單位，平均呎價亦相對較高；往後再以價單推售其他中小型分層單位時，價格會有明顯折讓，期望引起認購熱潮。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">他又指出，一手市場投資者入市比例由去年初的10%至20%，增至目前約30%至40%，個別收租旺區比例更達一半。今年新盤平均亦有30%買家來自內地，部分樓盤更超過一半。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15851633-%e4%bb%a3%e7%90%86%e6%96%99%e6%ac%a1%e5%ad%a3%e7%b4%8415%e6%96%b0%e7%9b%a4%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4-%e4%b8%80%e6%89%8b%e4%ba%a4%e6%8a%95%e6%96%99%e7%a9%a9%e5%ae%886000%e5%ae%97",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_PP_HK-PROPERTY_BP_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 08:21:15",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期高水約140點 重磅港股ADR幾全升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時12分升170點或0.66%，報25891點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報25896點，較香港上日現貨收市高144點或0.56%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣508.2元，較上日香港收市低0.31元或0.06%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣125元，較上日香港收市高2.13元或1.73%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣88.6元，較上日香港收市高0.56元或0.64%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣111元，較上日香港收市低0.69元或0.62%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣31.5元，較上日香港收市高0.18元或0.57%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣141.4元，較上日香港收市高2.54元或1.83%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣89.8元，較上日香港收市高1.34元或1.51%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣410.6元，較上日香港收市高2.38元或0.58%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣62.7元，較上日香港收市高0.42元或0.68%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣8.5元，較上日香港收市高0.05元或0.54%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報25900點，升181點，較上日恒指收市25752點，高水148點。科指期貨夜市收報4839點，較上日科指收市高水17點；國指期貨夜市收報8650點，較上日國指收市高水38點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15855010-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e7%b4%84140%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e5%b9%be%e5%85%a8%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 08:21:13",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日韓股市初段齊造好 兩市股指暫均升逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華爾街股市昨晚持續向上，帶動日韓股市今早初段反彈。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260212_FI_source-ap_KS.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/20260212_FI_source-ap_KS.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至香港時間上午約8時11分，日經平均指數升655點或1.17%，報56550點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">南韓首爾綜合指數暫升109點或1.89%，報5887點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15854991-%e6%97%a5%e9%9f%93%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%bd%8a%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd-%e5%85%a9%e5%b8%82%e8%82%a1%e6%8c%87%e6%9a%ab%e5%9d%87%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250625_FI_source-ap_Japan_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp",
